### Component Structure

- Follow Feature-First Architecture:
  ```
  src/app/
  ├── dashboard/
  │   ├── layout.tsx        # Shared dashboard layout
  │   ├── features/         # Feature-specific pages and components
  │   │   ├── todo-list/
  │   │   │   ├── page.tsx
  │   │   │   └── components/
  │   │   └── habit-tracker/
  │   │       ├── page.tsx
  │   │       └── components/
  │   └── components/       # Dashboard-specific shared components
  ├── components/           # Global shared components
  ├── lib/                  # Shared utilities and helpers
  └── types/               # TypeScript definitions
  ```

### Feature Organization Rules
- Keep features self-contained
- Use server components by default
- Isolate client components to smallest possible units
- Maintain consistent file naming (kebab-case)
- Include loading.tsx and error.tsx for each feature 